  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2><strong>Our partnership with Snow Camp</strong></h2>
<h4><strong>Inghams are committed to increasing exposure and opening up career opportunities for all young people in the UK. No matter your background, gender or ethnicity, we want everyone to be able to experience the joy of skiing and snowboarding.</strong></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Snow Camp is a life changing snow-sports programme for young people across the UK who are all in need of support. Some suffer from poor self-esteem, mental health struggles or are having a difficult time at home and/or at school.  Snow Camp is a lifeline providing vital opportunities and support to those who need it the most. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img style="width: 434.813px; height: 500px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13094453/snow-camp-logo.png?width=434.8127600554785&amp;height=500" alt="snowcamp" data-udi="umb://media/3f800021c4b84742bc64fa1921d013a3" /></span></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">What is Snow Camp: </span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">✔️ Working at indoor snow domes, young people learn how to ski or snowboard alongside life skills training, qualifications and mental health support.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">✔️ As part of their training young people also experience the mountains for the very first time on an annual residential.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">✔️ After a year of hard work they spend a week in the mountains shadowing instructors and gaining valuable snow experience.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Working with Snow Camp:</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are working with Snow Camp, to help break down barriers and broaden the horizons for young people in the UK. We are committed to:</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">✔️ </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">12 month internship in the Inghams and Esprit UK head office to give one of the 2023/24 Snow Camp apprentices first-hand experience of working in the industry.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">✔️ Inghams &amp; sister ski brand, Esprit, will host another group of young apprentices in the Alps in winter 2023/24 to give them exposure to life in the mountains</span></p>
</div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span></p>
<h4><strong>In January 2023, we took a group of young Snow Camp apprentices out to the mountains to give them a taste of life working as a seasonaire:</strong></h4>
<p><iframe width="100%" height="450" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3qLv_3veV7E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen="" title="YouTube video player"></iframe></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.snow-camp.org.uk/" target="_blank" title="Snowcamp"><strong>Find out more about Snow Camp &gt;&gt;</strong></a></h4>
<h4><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.workaseason.com/" target="_blank" title="Workaseason"><strong>Find out more about seasonal job opportunities with Inghams &amp; Esprit &gt;&gt;</strong></a></h4>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p><em><span style="font-weight: 400;">Snow Camp is part of youth Switch180 charity. Charity number 1101030 and OSCR SC043344</span></em></p>]]></bodyText>
